## Cell 4: Preprocess and Resize Images
```python
from PIL import Image
import glob
import torchvision.transforms as transforms

resize_transform = transforms.Resize((768, 1280))

for img_path in glob.glob(os.path.join(dataset_path, '*.jpg')):
    img = Image.open(img_path)
    img = resize_transform(img)
    img.save(img_path)  # save resized image
print('All images have been resized to 768x1280.')
```

